      "fluff": {
        "en": "Reaver Titans are vast god-machines possessed of truly devastating firepower. From the apocalypse missile launcher mounted on their carapace to their arm-mounted laser blaster, Reavers are more than capable of wiping out ground troops, their void shields and thick adamantine hulls nullifying all but the most piercing enemy strikes."
